B.arv=new A.dj("How do I import sessions from a spreadsheet?","Tap Import on the Import/Export screen and pick a CSV or Excel file from your device. TableLab will show a column mapping UI \u2014 drag or assign your spreadsheet's columns to the correct session fields. Confirm the mapping and the sessions will be imported.")
