B.ara=new A.dj("What is the Reads tab?","Reads is your private database of opponent notes. Add any player you've encountered and record tells, tendencies, bet-sizing patterns, or any observations from your time at the table with them.")
B.arz=new A.dj("How do I add a read?","Go to the Reads tab and tap the + button. Enter the player's name and your notes. You can add and edit notes over time as you encounter the player in future sessions.")
